00:42:14.270 --> 00:42:15.340
Say we get that.

00:42:15.340 --> 00:42:17.670
Say people are like,
OK, your book sold.

00:42:17.670 --> 00:42:20.840
We like you, but here's $15,000
for the advance of

00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:21.940
your first book.

00:42:21.940 --> 00:42:24.240
I mean, for us, that's
like, no.

00:42:24.240 --> 00:42:25.090
Absolutely not.

00:42:25.090 --> 00:42:27.370
We can put this out on our
own, and we will do much

00:42:27.370 --> 00:42:27.980
better than that.

00:42:27.980 --> 00:42:30.170
And have full control
over the cover, full

00:42:30.170 --> 00:42:31.490
