We get to hire our own
editor, who knows our

00:42:33.020 --> 00:42:34.580
stuff extremely well.

00:42:34.580 --> 00:42:36.480
So that has to get up
to a certain level.

00:42:36.480 --> 00:42:40.400
So that's the part I'm most
looking forward to, is seeing

00:42:40.400 --> 00:42:42.310
how things shake out when
you take a book into the

00:42:42.310 --> 00:42:42.940
marketplace.

00:42:42.940 --> 00:42:47.460
Because now as creators
in any stripe, you

00:42:47.460 --> 00:42:48.470
