00:43:26.820 --> 00:43:29.720
Because we're a media company.

00:43:29.720 --> 00:43:31.190
We're an entertainment
company.

00:43:31.190 --> 00:43:34.400
We sell advertising against our
content, and that's where

00:43:34.400 --> 00:43:35.690
most of our revenue
