00:45:24.490 --> 00:45:24.750
SCOTT SIGLER: Yeah.

00:45:24.750 --> 00:45:27.200
So how do I get the ideas?

00:45:27.200 --> 00:45:31.110
And then once I had the idea,
how do I massage that idea up

00:45:31.110 --> 00:45:33.490
into an actual full-blown book,
and what is the process

00:45:33.490 --> 00:45:34.160
involved in that?

00:45:34.160 --> 00:45:35.500
Yeah?

00:45:35.500 --> 00:45:37.590
The idea is, I have
