00:45:41.050 --> 00:45:43.000
span, and ideas just--

00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:43.540
all day.

00:45:43.540 --> 00:45:45.320
I wrote three books
on the walk here.

00:45:45.320 --> 00:45:46.470
And I'm not even kidding.

00:45:46.470 --> 00:45:49.000
I passed a gated library,
and I'm like, oh,

00:45:49.000 --> 00:45:49.520
that's a cool place.

00:45:49.520 --> 00:45:50.520
What can we do with that?

00:45:50.520 --> 00:45:55.980
So trying to try to control the
overwhelming amount of,

00:45:55.980 --> 00:45:58.740
this is the greatest idea I've
ever had, I have to stop

00:45:58.740 --> 00:46:00.520
